instruction: Please provide an evaluation of the potential effect of global economic restart and vaccines on the value and other factors using our adaptive multi-factor model.
output: Based on our adaptive multi-factor model, the potential effect of global economic restart and vaccines on value and other factors is still subject to evaluation. However, we anticipate some positive effects on the value factor, while other factors such as quality, yield, and low volatility may continue to remain underweight. We will continue to monitor this closely and provide updates as necessary.
